ts demonstrate the high efficiency of $0^-$ state detection by the\nparity-transfer reaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 04:48:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2020 01:46:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-04"}
