s. As observed high-order\nminibands and LL reconstruction qualitatively match our simulated results. Our\nfindings highlight the synergistic effect of minibands in transport, thus\npresenting a new opportunity for graphene electronic devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 09:15:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-31"}
