ucts that do not satisfy associativity\nand distributive law with respect to the $d$ operator. A proper formulation of\ntheories that contain higher order differential forms in the context of Regge\nCalculus is then still lacking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 10:26:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-09"}
