ing inputs and outputs benefit experts in the\ndevelopment of deep traffic prediction models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 14:32:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 08:18:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2020 14:20:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-08"}
